      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        User Submissions
      </h2>

      <p>
        If you submit a tip, document, message, correction, photograph, or other material, you represent that you have the right to submit it and that your submission does not knowingly violate any law or the rights of others.
